  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Rock",
    "Metal"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 7,
  "lyrics": "Is there no matter of pain? Is it coming? You know it's coming That line You crossed a thousand times They come back to you Dressed in new Dressed in different Dressed in different things Are you gonna hold back or do what should they do? Only you Can you feel the leaves rolling down? You watch the raining tides arise I know that you feel the wind Know that you don't understand Only Swimming energies Inside your mind But know that I'm here Navigating the same waters I've run Enough times Yet I just hear with me I see some line above the trees Through the forest of the dark You get stuck with inside your mind It's not a heartless It's not crime It's just the things of you That see the things that relate to you Blue When the sky is orange I know you find me there Even though Nuclear meltdown's right around the corner Don't push too hard Just let go And stay in the groove of the beam Inside your heart That guides you to the things That makes you open free Keep it alive As you fall between the seams On what you think is right A hypocritical thought You fight yourself at night I've been there Many times over The course of what you think you can attain What you end and what you know is that It's all in the name Or what you call yourself in that mind frame And I just want you to know that",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 2.9800000190734863,
      "text": "Is there no matter of pain?",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 5.099999904632568,
      "text": "Is it coming?",
      "start": 4.739999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 7.760000228881836,
      "text": "You know it's coming",
      "start": 6.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 8.960000038146973,
      "text": "That line",
      "start": 7.760000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 11.800000190734863,
      "text": "You crossed a thousand times",
      "start": 9.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 14,
      "text": "They come back to you",
      "start": 11.800000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 14.539999961853027,
      "text": "Dressed in new",
      "start": 14
    },
    {
      "end": 15.859999656677246,
      "text": "Dressed in different",
      "start": 14.539999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 18,
      "text": "Dressed in different things",
      "start": 15.859999656677246
    },
    {
      "end": 23.3799991607666,
      "text": "Are you gonna hold back or do what should they do?",
      "start": 18.559999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 25.760000228881836,
      "text": "Only you",
      "start": 24.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 29.399999618530273,
      "text": "Can you feel the leaves rolling down?",
      "start": 25.760000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 31.8799991607666,
      "text": "You watch the raining tides arise",
      "start": 29.799999237060547
    },
    {
      "end": 33.7599983215332,
      "text": "I know that you feel the wind",
      "start": 31.8799991607666
    },
    {
      "end": 37.040000915527344,
      "text": "Know that you don't understand",
      "start": 34.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 37.7599983215332,
      "text": "Only",
      "start": 37.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 40.7400016784668,
      "text": "Swimming energies",
      "start": 38.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 42.040000915527344,
      "text": "Inside your mind",
      "start": 40.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 43.7599983215332,
      "text": "But know that I'm here",
      "start": 42.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 47.400001525878906,
      "text": "Navigating the same waters",
      "start": 45.279998779296875
    },
    {
      "end": 48.400001525878906,
      "text": "I've run",
      "start": 47.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 50.900001525878906,
      "text": "Enough times",
      "start": 49.220001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 51.86000061035156,
      "text": "Yet",
      "start": 50.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 54.099998474121094,
      "text": "I just hear with me",
      "start": 51.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 58,
      "text": "I see some line above the trees",
      "start": 54.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 60.97999954223633,
      "text": "Through the forest of the dark",
      "start": 58.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 63.52000045776367,
      "text": "You get stuck with inside your mind",
      "start": 60.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 65.05999755859375,
      "text": "It's not a heartless",
      "start": 63.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 66.05999755859375,
      "text": "It's not crime",
      "start": 65.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 68.05999755859375,
      "text": "It's just the things of you",
      "start": 66.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 72.0199966430664,
      "text": "That see the things that relate to you",
      "start": 69.0999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 72.9000015258789,
      "text": "Blue",
      "start": 72.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 75.12000274658203,
      "text": "When the sky is orange",
      "start": 72.9000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 77.5999984741211,
      "text": "I know you find me there",
      "start": 75.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 79.08000183105469,
      "text": "Even though",
      "start": 77.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 82.31999969482422,
      "text": "Nuclear meltdown's right around the corner",
      "start": 79.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 84.73999786376953,
      "text": "Don't push too hard",
      "start": 83.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 87.81999969482422,
      "text": "Just let go",
      "start": 85.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 91.66000366210938,
      "text": "And stay in the groove of the beam",
      "start": 87.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 92.86000061035156,
      "text": "Inside your heart",
      "start": 91.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 94.80000305175781,
      "text": "That guides you to the things",
      "start": 92.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 96.31999969482422,
      "text": "That makes you open free",
      "start": 94.80000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 99.37999725341797,
      "text": "Keep it alive",
      "start": 97.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 101.91999816894531,
      "text": "As you fall between the seams",
      "start": 99.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 103.73999786376953,
      "text": "On what you think is right",
      "start": 101.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 105.55999755859375,
      "text": "A hypocritical thought",
      "start": 103.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 107.86000061035156,
      "text": "You fight yourself at night",
      "start": 105.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 110.33999633789062,
      "text": "I've been there",
      "start": 108.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 112.5199966430664,
      "text": "Many times over",
      "start": 110.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 116.77999877929688,
      "text": "The course of what you think you can attain",
      "start": 113.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 119.87999725341797,
      "text": "What you end and what you know is that",
      "start": 116.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 121.33999633789062,
      "text": "It's all in the name",
      "start": 119.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 126.13999938964844,
      "text": "Or what you call yourself in that mind frame",
      "start": 122.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 128.6199951171875,
      "text": "And I just want you to know that",
      "start": 126.13999938964844
    }
  ],
